tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE program_impact_analysis (
  program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  total_participants INT,
  outcome_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE impact_program (
  program_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
  program_description TEXT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  impact_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE outcome_reporting (
  report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id UUID REFERENCES impact_program(program_id),
  report_date DATE,
  total_participants INT,
  outcomes_description TEXT,
  report_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE program_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_id INT NOT NULL,
    outcome_id INT NOT NULL,
    report_date DATE,
    report_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE impact_reports (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name TEXT,
    outcome TEXT,
    impact_level INT
)
